ftestSetNameOfGame( sqrfree, `"
Usage: sqrfree [<options>] [<envSpec>] [sort=<flag>] <f>
  computes squarefree decomposition of canonical form <f>.
  If optional <flag> is set, squarefree factors are returned
  sorted by multiplicity.
"'`' )

